Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: President Kennedy had Just had a Nasty Shock
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00sxbxb
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 20 Sep 2002
Alistair Cooke considers the Cuban missile crisis, weapons inspections in Iraq and the scandal of Richard Nixon's membership of an all white golf club.